msgid "Why?"
msgstr "Perché?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/13_Scouting.cfg:416
msgid ""
"First of all, because our people at Freetown aren't ready to have an "
"Akladian leader. Second, because Bor Cryne would send his entire army to "
"pursue us if he heard so much as a whisper of the name Gawen Hagarthen."
msgstr ""
"Poiché la nostra gente a Freetown non è pronta ad avere un capo di Akladia. "
"E, in secondo luogo, perché allora Bor Cryne manderebbe tutto il suo "
"esercito a inseguirci."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/13_Scouting.cfg:417
msgid ""
"Gaumhaldric... so, is this why my son is not shaving? He wants to hide his "
"real identity under a beard?"
msgstr ""
"Gaumhaldric.. Ecco, dunque, perché il mio figlio non si rade? Vuole "
"nascondere la sua vera identità sotto la barba?"

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/13_Scouting.cfg:418
msgid ""
"No, no, no. He HAS to have a beard. All of our great Wesnothian kings had "
"beards!"
msgstr "Nonono. Deve portare la barba perché tutti i grandi re hanno la barba."

#. [objectives]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/13_Scouting.cfg:430
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "This is a large-scale map, where you may choose a way to go. Move Gawen "
#| "to any of the signpost or any other location to trigger moving to the "
