#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/14e_Saorduc_Swamps.cfg:264
msgid "Oh, I hate lizards."
msgstr "Oh, io odio le lucertole."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/14e_Saorduc_Swamps.cfg:265
msgid ""
"They will be good practice for our soldiers. And maybe they know something."
msgstr ""
"Sarà un buon esercizio per i nostri soldati. E forse sanno pure qualcosa."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/14e_Saorduc_Swamps.cfg:268
