msgstr "Mi dirai tutto quello che sai sugli orchi."

#. [event]
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/14e_Saorduc_Swamps.cfg:403
msgid ""
"And I thought this day sssstarted ssssuch beautifully... What orcs? They "
