msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#. "this" refers to the gallows to which Lorin has just moved:
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/02_Fighting_for_Passage.cfg:400
msgid "I suppose we will find some use for this in near future."
