#: A_New_Order/scenarios/05_The_Swamp_Things.cfg:282
#: A_New_Order/scenarios/05_The_Swamp_Things.cfg:324
msgid ""
"Interesting. Speak, and maybe I will spare your worthless head, inhuman "
